{"tid":744681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬國三項鐵人賽失蹤者遺體尋獲 相信為香港男子","createTime":"2018-07-16T06:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T08:38:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6462b45b34d303956e0157ae348486d2afee02","tid":744681,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:27:56.000Z","msg":"香港男子袁志遠（音譯）周日（15日）在馬來西亞參加「狄臣港三項鐵人國際賽」期間，懷疑被大浪捲走失蹤。當地傳媒報道，失蹤者遺體周一（16日）已尋獲，導致這場國際賽的死亡人數增加至2人。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，救援隊當日早上6時30分繼續展開搜索行動，並在7時57分接獲漁夫報告，指在加弄島發現死者的遺體。當局在8時許成功把遺體帶上岸，隨即送往附近醫院。<br />\n<br />\n除了一名香港參賽者出事之外，另一名華裔男子譚威榮（Tharm Wai Weng，音譯）亦在游泳項目中遭大浪捲走斃命。國家青年體育部部長賽沙迪表示，將成立特別調查小組，調查三項鐵人賽是否符合當局標準。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WJbWrl9iJb7ucemjf_dikg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/f6e62af530d12e7e8ca393151fbc7e97\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWJbWrl9iJb7ucemjf_dikg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Ff6e62af530d12e7e8ca393151fbc7e97&h=3b2ccaa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%89%E9%A0%85%E9%90%B5%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%BD%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E8%80%85%E9%81%BA%E9%AB%94%E5%B0%8B%E7%8D%B2%E3%80%80%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90-025413817.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%25A0%2585%25E9%2590%25B5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2581%25BA%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%25B0%258B%25E7%258D%25B2%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590-025413817.html&d=OBl%2FAhGcvaNzpESIBU6PjP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b91f07ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%89%E9%A0%85%E9%90%B5%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%BD%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E8%80%85%E9%81%BA%E9%AB%94%E5%B0%8B%E7%8D%B2%E3%80%80%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90-025413817.html</a>"},{"pid":"bc85900c5098ef26f5ebcc1359e91ac6997e15e5","tid":744681,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T08:09:50.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"2f057991caa843be454882cad661f5ae0f9df84f","tid":744681,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T08:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cb4747c13fbb0748b506e826ab55252f930419","tid":744681,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T08:36:17.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e257b2287c72fa006c8ab719a739e1809f6a6ce","tid":744681,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T08:38:03.000Z","msg":"求仁得仁"}]}